{"tid":1866680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 做文宣嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-02-06T23:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T23:40:07.000Z","uid":149188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"00908071a1419ef564c75cfa86d37657d1792322","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:36:37.000Z","msg":"Sor有少少長<br />\n<br />\n連儂牆 Airdrop我唔會話係最好嘅地方整文宣<br />\n因為做得藍絲好少睇新新聞 多數要番長時間工<br />\n淨係靠TVB同whatsapp收新聞<br />\n<br />\n整文宣最好嘅地方一定係Facebook啲藍絲group<br />\n果到整合曬最痴線嘅藍絲<br />\n放個例子比大家睇<br />\n呢張圖我係其中一個group down落嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NY16bqn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNY16bqn.png&h=94e66948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>明明人地醫護由頭到尾得2個訴求</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.封關<br />\n2.確保醫管局提供足夠物資比佢地打扙</span><br />\n<br />\n但佢地出張咁嘅圖藍絲又真係信到十足<br />\n所以我想請做開文宣嘅巴絲用假account又好真account都好 用平時連儂牆嘅精神係佢啲fake news下面撕一貼十<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/113401456730163/posts/189300612473580/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F113401456730163%2Fposts%2F189300612473580%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWQy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=832f1011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/113401456730163/posts/189300612473580/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/486392624735448/posts/3591617464212933/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F486392624735448%2Fposts%2F3591617464212933%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWQy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=452eb5ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/486392624735448/posts/3591617464212933/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n我知大家好唔想見到對家嘅文宣 但你唔睇又點樣幫佢地睇到真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以得閒咪follow 下佢地啲group留下啲真相比佢地知<br />\n記住一定要有數據support 因為佢地最怕見到真相"},{"pid":"abc208f6920d45836f280d75373fc3c60485ccf9","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"b601c270d6b7fa5ba121582c49c14c29c97cf111","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:37:48.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"439d6737c85d5bb50808e34baf2582f51fd07125","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:38:01.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"91b365efe898fea2eedd69ea1e766ed1275a625d","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:38:11.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"3c50b6f8f95c1bf899e67051db6582eb4d49f0c8","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:38:25.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"6d021455e263e554efaa1526d589dc5df920ef0d","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:39:07.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"eb048ef073eb4dc1e756658f37b353c2f10f714c","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:39:21.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"6b51ebbd0abaad7b8e5000521011622cfaa20f6e","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:39:31.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"0e02c2708a8a102efb128c128a5dd82eef9201b9","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:39:57.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"dab9fc7122a905a06048f2224eb867b72168a168","tid":1866680,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:40:07.000Z","msg":"10/10"}]}